    content: "",
    faqs: [
      { q: "How much food does the Petlibro Granary hold?", a: "The 3L version holds about 12-15 cups of kibble, good for 10-15 days for one cat. The 5L version holds 20-25 cups, lasting up to 20 days." },
      { q: "Does the Petlibro camera work at night?", a: "Yes — the night vision is excellent, with clear black-and-white video in complete darkness. Motion alerts also work at night." },
      { q: "Can I use Petlibro Granary without the app?", a: "The schedule requires initial app setup via Wi-Fi. Once programmed, the feeder continues on schedule even if your phone is off. Manual feeding buttons are available on the unit." },
