  },
  "wopet-automatic-feeder-review": {
    title: "WOPET Automatic Feeder Review 2026 — Best Budget Smart Feeder?",
    description: "Hands-on WOPET automatic feeder review: testing the 6L capacity, app reliability, portion accuracy, and whether it's the best value feeder under $100.",
    productId: "wopet-automatic",
    verdict: "At $89, the WOPET is the best value smart feeder on the market. The 6L hopper is massive (largest in its class), the built-in battery backup is a thoughtful touch, and it handles up to 10 meals per day reliably. You sacrifice camera, build quality, and app polish — but for pure scheduled feeding, it's unbeatable at the price.",
