    faqs: [
      { q: "Is the WOPET feeder suitable for large dogs?", a: "Yes — the 6L hopper holds about 25-30 cups of kibble, enough for a large dog for 5-7 days. Portion sizes can be set from 1 to 20 portions per meal (about 5g per portion)." },
