  },
  "pioneer-pet-raindrop-review": {
    title: "Pioneer Pet Raindrop Fountain Review 2026 — The Timeless Budget Classic",
    description: "We review the Pioneer Pet Raindrop — a stainless steel, no-frills pet fountain that's been a bestseller for over a decade. Is it still worth buying in 2026?",
